# Git Rules
- NEVER run `git commit`, `git push`, or `git stash` unless the user explicitly asks you to.
- NEVER amend, rebase, or force-push unless the user explicitly asks you to.
- You may run read-only git commands (`git status`, `git diff`, `git log`, etc.) freely.
